{"tid":2441709,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"劏房波去信WSJ反對剔除香港獨立排名, WSJ”唔好當人白痴, 接受香港=支那”","createTime":"2021-03-11T01:15:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T12:27:33.000Z","uid":123774,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ffa01ab4e2dc80b33aad8ab14aaa150f295e87a7","tid":2441709,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T01:15:17.000Z","msg":"香港被美國傳統基金會剔除經濟自由度指數，將與澳門一起列入中國一併評分，財政司司長陳茂波去信《華爾街日報》對決定表示遺憾，再重申香港擁有「一國兩制」保障自由。《華爾街日報》編輯部今刊出評論文章回應，<span class=\"red\">直接籲陳茂波不必再遊說國際社會香港沒有改變，並指中共已對外宣稱1984年簽署的《中英聯合聲明》為已過去的歷史文件，換言之其保證的「一國兩制」亦不存在，「我們對陳先生的建議是，不要再試圖讓世界相信香港像從前一樣，而應接受現實，現在真正掌管香港的是中國國家主席習近平。」</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210311/BSAQQV4FIVDWJHRKX26WAOGYAM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210311%2FBSAQQV4FIVDWJHRKX26WAOGYAM%2F&d=86rwbh%2BN0C2BU4li7ttIPq%2FFu68%2BWP7gD6%2BC1gzqbK8%3D&h=b307d175\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20210311%2FBSAQQV4FIVDWJHRKX26WAOGYAM%2F&h=a65b53b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20210311/BSAQQV4FIVDWJHRKX26WAOGYAM/</a>"},{"pid":"c9c6915cd4ba04bf5517980549bd84f97d3ef337","tid":2441709,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:26:06.000Z","msg":"自己衝出嚟柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e8a9e629c152709048b4c9466ecc2ae1cac9b5f","tid":2441709,"uid":387826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T12:27:33.000Z","msg":"正確做法係去信翠太大"}]}